Package org.magicdgs.readtools.documentation Description

Custom Barclay-based Javadoc classes used for generating ReadTools help/documentation.

NOTE: Classes and methods in this package are intended to be called by Gradle/Javadoc only, and should not be called by methods that are used by the runtime. Dependends on com.sun.javadoc classes, which may not be present since they're not provided as part of the normal runtime classpath.
